@endnode

@node RX_SHOWPIC "AGAiff - ARexx Commands"
SYNTAX
	ShowPic

FUNCTION
	Puts the picture screen to front. If no picture screen is open,
	this function is no-op.

INPUTS
	None

RESULTS
